    "description": "审判军团是一款2.5D银河战士恶魔城游戏，一款动作有深度的成长型农场RPG游戏。 你必须躲在人类中间，与占领世界的狼人公会进行一场孤独的战争。 白天管理老旅馆，晚上攻击狼人公会，赚取收入，开发旅馆，重建审判军团是你的职责。 但是现在你已经失去了所有的能力以及对过去的记忆。 你必须探索自己的头脑，以重新获得失去的记忆和力量。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>横版卷轴战斗与开放式探索的融合</strong></h2>运用取消、格挡等多种动作联动和动作系统，与手持自动武器的敌人展开精彩绝伦的剑术对战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/2798e99fda1fa154acbf9919241a79ef.poster.avif?t=1715236400\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/2798e99fda1fa154acbf9919241a79ef.webm?t=1715236400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/2798e99fda1fa154acbf9919241a79ef.mp4?t=1715236400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/ca3dccd863d4f072c3274118e2f97c37.poster.avif?t=1715236400\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/ca3dccd863d4f072c3274118e2f97c37.webm?t=1715236400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/ca3dccd863d4f072c3274118e2f97c37.mp4?t=1715236400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/2259f88351b7cda7ab1dfd6e08d89364.poster.avif?t=1715236400\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/2259f88351b7cda7ab1dfd6e08d89364.webm?t=1715236400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.a