codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/9267275f620d7565a61d894f5dbfef8a.mp4?t=1715236400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>破旧旅馆的重生,通往审判军团的故事</strong></h2>作为酒店的 CEO，你必须管理和发展这家旧酒店，并最终将其用作审判军团的藏身之处。 开发酒店以聚集更多的军团成员，并利用他们的能力赢得与狼人公会的战争。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/a54e0d5b0cb686f66d5ad6ffc01df257.poster.avif?t=1715236400\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/a54e0d5b0cb686f66d5ad6ffc01df257.webm?t=1715236400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/a54e0d5b0cb686f66d5ad6ffc01df257.mp4?t=1715236400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/3051324c22eeafedb334549bb4f99fd3.poster.avif?t=1715236400\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/3051324c22eeafedb334549bb4f99fd3.webm?t=1715236400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264780/extras/3051324c22eeafedb334549bb4f99fd3.mp4?t=1715236400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
